'''热带风暴弗洛西'''（{{lang-en|Tropical Storm Flossie}}）是[[2013年太平洋飓风季|2013年太平洋飓风季]]形成的第六个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]和第六场获命名的风暴，于同年7月下旬在[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]产生暴风雨。系统源自7月9日离开非洲西海岸的[[东风波|东风波]]，穿越大西洋期间基本没有发展，于7月18日经[[中美洲|中美洲]]进入东太平洋。由于外界环境有利，系统稳步发展，到[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]7月25日早上6点已有充分组织而成为热带低气压，再于六小时后进一步增强成热带风暴并获名“弗洛西”。气旋继续西进，于7月27日达到[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]110公里的最高强度后进入中太平洋。受[[风切变|上层风]]的不利影响，风暴开始减弱，于7月30日降级成热带低气压，并且到{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}当天中午12点时已在[[考艾岛|考艾岛]]东北方向退化成残留[[低气压|低气压区]]。

风暴逼近前，[[夏威夷群岛|夏威夷群岛]]多个岛屿进入[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋警告]]生效状态，此外，气象机构预测气旋产生的降水可能超过300毫米，所以还发出山洪预警。许多港口及其它设施中止向公众开放，有关部门开设避难所，供人们前来躲避。弗洛西逐渐逼近夏威夷州，气象部门预计它有可能会是20年来首场[[登陆_(气象学)|直接袭击]]夏威夷的热带风暴，但气旋实际上尚未登陆就已大幅减弱。风暴在该州产生大浪，引发轻度[[海蚀|海滩侵蚀]]。阵风时速超过热带风暴标准，刮倒许多电线杆和树木，当地数千居民家中因此停电数天。气旋还令[[夏威夷岛|夏威夷岛]]普遍降下上百毫米雨量，其中最高降雨量发生在[[怀厄莱阿莱山|怀厄莱阿莱山]]，达235毫米。风暴没有造成人员丧生，但有一人因闪电受伤。气旋引发的闪电一共造成价值约2万4000美元（2013年[[美元|美元]]）损失。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Flossie 2013 track.png}}
2013年7月9日，有[[东风波|东风波]]离开非洲西海岸进入大西洋并快速西进，经过大洋期间没有显著发展，再于7月18日经过[[中美洲|中美洲]]，不久后进入东太平洋<ref name="Ftcr">{{cite report | author1 = John P. Cangialosi | author2 = Derek Wroe | title = Tropical Cyclone Report: Tropical Storm Flossie | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP062013_Flossie.pdf | publisher = [[美国国家海洋和大气管理局|National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration]] | work = [[国家飓风中心|National Hurricane Center]] | date = 2013-11-04 | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | location = [[迈阿密|Miami]], [[佛罗里达州|Florida]] | format = [[便携式文档格式|PDF]] | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304105534/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/data/tcr/EP062013_Flossie.pdf | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。7月21日清晨，东太平洋有与东风波关联的广阔[[低气压|低气压区]]形成，[[国家飓风中心|美国国家飓风中心]]开始监控这片接下来逐渐发展成[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]的[[热带扰动|扰动天气]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Todd B. Kimberlain | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201307211140.txt | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-21 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304110942/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201307211140.txt | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | location = Miami, Florida | format = [[文本文件|TXT]] | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = no }}</ref>。之后几天，系统内的降水和[[雷暴|雷暴]]活动逐渐凝聚，美国国家飓风中心在热带天气展望中指出，扰动天气发展成热带气旋的可能性很大<ref>{{cite report | author = John P. Cangialosi | title = Tropical Weather Outlook | location = Miami, Florida | format = TXT | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201307241731.txt | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-24 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304202048/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/text/TWOEP/2013/TWOEP.201307241731.txt | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | accessdate = 2016-07-19 }}</ref>，不过，7月24日清晨的卫星数据表明系统内还缺乏明确环流，尚不足以归类成热带气旋。到了这天晚上，可视和微波卫星图像都表明旋涡结构有所改善，气象机构因此把位于[[下加利福尼亚半岛|下加利福尼亚半岛]]最南端西南偏西方向约1575公里洋面的扰动天气归类成热带低气压。<ref name="Ftcr" />

成为热带低气压后，气旋在[[美国西南部|美国西南部]]上空中层[[高压脊|高压脊]]的影响下朝西和[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向前进。此后几小时里，深层对流的覆盖范围和强度都逐渐提高，[[德沃夏克分析法|卫星强度估算值]]也相应增大<ref>{{cite report | author = John P. Cangialosi | title = Tropical Storm Flossie Discussion Number 2 | location = Miami, Florida | format = SHTML | url = http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep06/ep062013.discus.002.shtml | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = National Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-25 | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304205337/http://www.nhc.noaa.gov/archive/2013/ep06/ep062013.discus.002.shtml | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>，美国国家飓风中心于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]7月25日早上6点将其升级成热带风暴，并以“弗洛西”（{{lang|en|Flossie}}）命名。由于外界环境风切变少、[[海面温度|海面温度]]高，风暴之后两天逐渐强化，到了7月27日清晨，可视卫星图像上已时断时续地出现中层[[风眼|风眼]]，微波卫星图像上的风眼清晰可见。{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}中午12点，弗洛西达到[[最大持续风速|最大持续风速]]每小时110公里，最低[[气压|气压]]994[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]；29.35[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度。风暴接下来穿越[[西经140度线|西经140度线]]进入中太平洋，[[中太平洋飓风中心|中太平洋飓风中心]]接手预警职责。受上层[[低压槽|低压槽]]生成[[风切变|上层风]]的不利影响，气旋无法进一步组织，并且很快就开始呈现减弱趋势。<ref name="Ftcr" />

受强烈风切变和水温降低的共同影响，弗洛西关联的深层对流逐渐减弱，卫星图像也变得模糊，气象机构因此预测风暴会继续减弱<ref>{{cite report | author = Robert T. Burke | title = Tropical Storm Flossie Discussion Number 12 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2013/TCDCP1.EP062013.012.1307272036 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-27 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103014417/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2013/TCDCP1.EP062013.012.1307272036 | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | location = [[檀香山|Honolulu]], [[夏威夷州|Hawaii]] }}</ref>。但由于上层风短暂衰减，气旋实际上在{{lang|en|UTC}}7月28日中午12点达到风力时速100公里的第二波强度高峰。受西北方向的[[反气旋|反气旋]]影响，弗洛西上空的风切变到次日已明显增多，环流还开始受到干燥空气的侵蚀<ref>{{cite report | author = Pete Donaldson | title = Tropical Storm Flossie Discussion Number 18 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2013/TCDCP1.EP062013.018.1307290904 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-28 | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | location = Honolulu, Hawaii | archive-date = 2016-03-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304061940/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2013/TCDCP1.EP062013.018.1307290904 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。下层旋涡变得暴露在外，[[外流边界|外流边界]]和之前的对流爆发都令低气压的发展受阻<ref>{{cite report | author = Robert T. Burke | title = Tropical Depression Flossie Discussion Number 21 | location = Honolulu, Hawaii | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2013/TCDCP1.EP062013.021.1307300242 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304064714/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2013/TCDCP1.EP062013.021.1307300242 | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref><ref>{{cite report | author = Pete Donaldson | title = Post-Tropical Cyclone Flossie Discussion Number 23 | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | location = Honolulu, Hawaii | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304081210/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2013/TCDCP1.EP062013.023.1307301445 | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2013/TCDCP1.EP062013.023.1307301445 | deadurl = no | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | work = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | date = 2013-07-30 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。{{lang|en|UTC}}7月30日凌晨0点，弗洛西降级成热带低气压，卫星图像上的气旋环流已经连续12小时难以区分后，气象部门宣布中心位于[[考艾岛|考艾岛]]北岸近海的弗洛西已退化成残留低气压区<ref name="Ftcr" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Tropical_Storm_Flossie_2013-07-29_2045Z.jpg|thumb]]
风暴进入中太平洋后，[[夏威夷县|夏威夷县]]和[[茂宜县|茂宜县]]于7月27日收到[[热带气旋警告|热带风暴观察预警]]<ref>{{cite report | author = Robert T. Burke | work = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2013-07-27 | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | title = Tropical Storm Flossie Advisory Number 13 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2013/WEB_TCPCP1.EP062013.013.1307280232.php | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055822/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2013/WEB_TCPCP1.EP062013.013.1307280232.php | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>，再于数小时后升级成热带风暴警告，同时[[欧胡岛|欧胡岛]]进入热带风暴观察预警生效状态<ref>{{cite report | author = Thomas R. Birchard Jr. | work = Central Pacific Hurricane Center | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | date = 2013-07-27 | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | type = Report | deadurl = no | url = http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2013/WEB_TCPCP1.EP062013.014.1307280903.php | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304054219/http://www.prh.noaa.gov/cphc/tcpages/archive/2013/WEB_TCPCP1.EP062013.014.1307280903.php | title = Tropical Storm Flossie Advisory Number 14 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 }}</ref>。气象机构预计气旋会在沿途降下暴雨，局部地区降雨量高达380毫米，因此从7月29日到30日向夏威夷全州发布山洪预警<ref>{{cite news | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | publisher = [[CBS新闻|CBS News]] | date = 2013-07-28 | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | title = Tropical Storm Flossie yields flood warnings in Hawaii | archivedate = 2016-03-09 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.cbsnews.com/news/tropical-storm-flossie-yields-flood-warnings-in-hawaii/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160309055250/http://www.cbsnews.com/news/tropical-storm-flossie-yields-flood-warnings-in-hawaii/ }}</ref>。茂宜县当局启动应急预案，县内所有公园停止向公众开放<ref name="Maui">{{cite news | title = Maui Activates Emergency Operations Center, All County Facilities to Close Monday | newspaper = The Maui News | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160322045453/http://mauinow.com/2013/07/28/maui-activates-emergency-operations-center-all-county-facilities-to-close-monday/ | archivedate = 2016-03-22 | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | date = 2013-07-28 | url = http://mauinow.com/2013/07/28/maui-activates-emergency-operations-center-all-county-facilities-to-close-monday/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。[[夏威夷岛|夏威夷岛]]所有的法院和高校均予关闭，[[夏威夷州州长|夏威夷州州长]][[尼尔·阿伯克龙比|尼尔·阿伯克龙比]]宣布该州进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]。全州共有三座港口关闭，其中夏威夷岛两处，茂宜岛一处<ref name="USA Today">{{cite news | title = Tropical Storm Flossie takes aim on Hawaii | url = http://www.usatoday.com/story/weather/2013/07/29/tropical-storm-flossie-hawaii-honolulu/2595393/ | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | work = [[今日美国|USA Today]] | date = 2013-07-29 | archivedate = 2015-05-25 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150525053912/http://www.usatoday.com/story/weather/2013/07/29/tropical-storm-flossie-hawaii-honolulu/2595393/ | deadurl = no }}</ref>。有关部门预计弗洛西会成为1992年以来首场登陆夏威夷州的热带风暴，所以在全州各地共开设11间避难所，其中茂宜岛四处，欧胡岛七处<ref name="WPTV1">{{cite news | title = Tropical Storm Flossie weakens, brings heavy rains to Hawaii | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | newspaper = WPTV News | date = 2013-07-29 | url = http://www.wptv.com/news/national/tropical-storm-flossie-weakens-brings-heavy-rains-to-hawaii | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160719154141/http://www.wptv.com/news/national/tropical-storm-flossie-weakens-brings-heavy-rains-to-hawaii | archive-date = 2016-07-19 | dead-url = yes }}</ref>，共有177人前来躲避<ref>{{cite news |title=PB's Disaster Awareness Report July 31, 2013 |archivedate=2014-01-02 |deadurl=yes |date=2013-07-31 |url=http://www.pbdisasterservices.com/pdfs/news_publications/daily_dart/daily%20dart_20130731.pdf |publisher=PB Disaster Services |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6MKsTiT9e?url=http://www.pbdisasterservices.com/pdfs/news_publications/daily_dart/daily%20dart_20130731.pdf |work=Parsons Brinckerhoff |accessdate=2014-01-02 }}</ref>。[[考艾县|考艾县]][[哈纳雷_(夏威夷州)|哈纳雷]]（{{lang|en|Hanalei}}）和瓦伊帕（{{lang|en|Waipa}}）原计划的停水作业因风暴来袭延期<ref>{{cite news | title = County of Kauai prepares for tropical storm Flossie | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | date = 2013-07-29 | agency = Khon2 | url = http://khon2.com/2013/07/29/county-of-kauai-prepares-for-tropical-storm-flossie/ | archivedate = 2016-04-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160422024052/http://khon2.com/2013/07/29/county-of-kauai-prepares-for-tropical-storm-flossie/ | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。

弗洛西还在海上时就在夏威夷州大部分海岸沿线产生大浪<ref>{{cite news | archivedate = 2013-11-15 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131115130758/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-29/storm-flossie-may-be-first-to-hit-hawaii-since-1992.html | title = Storm Flossie May Be First to Hit Hawaii Since 1992 | accessdate = 2013-11-15 | newspaper = Bloomberg | date = 2013-07-29 | author = Brian K. Sullivan | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-07-29/storm-flossie-may-be-first-to-hit-hawaii-since-1992.html }}</ref>。虽然最后是在夏威夷岛近海掠过，但强烈的阵风依然刮倒不少树木，还导致多条输电线缆中断，[[卡胡卢伊|卡胡卢伊]]测得的阵风时速达到76公里，为全岛最高。全州有上万居民失去供电，其中大部分生活在茂宜岛和夏威夷岛。<ref name="Ftcr" />多个岛上降下暴雨，[[哈莱亚卡拉火山|哈莱亚卡拉火山]]仅一小时就测得76到102毫米雨量<ref>{{cite news | title = Thousands on Maui, Big Island without electricity | url = http://khon2.com/2013/07/29/maui-residents-feel-impact-of-flossie/ | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304103732/http://khon2.com/2013/07/29/maui-residents-feel-impact-of-flossie/ | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | date = 2013-07-29 | author = Brianne Randle | agency = Khon2 | archivedate = 2016-03-04 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。茂宜岛东部的考波峡测得130毫米降雨总量<ref name="Rain">{{cite news | title = Flossie may leave a going-away present of afternoon showers | accessdate = 2013-12-12 | newspaper = Honolulu Star-advertiser | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131212042332/http://www.staradvertiser.com/news/breaking/20130730_Flossie_may_leave_a_goingawy_present_of_afternoon_showers.html?id=217577521 | author = Craig Gima | date = 2013-07-30 | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.staradvertiser.com/news/breaking/20130730_Flossie_may_leave_a_goingawy_present_of_afternoon_showers.html?id=217577521 | archivedate = 2013-12-12 }}</ref>，[[怀厄莱阿莱山|怀厄莱阿莱山]]则在风暴期间降下235毫米雨量，为全州最高<ref name="Ftcr" />。茂宜岛有一名男子因闪电受伤<ref>{{cite news | title = Zapped Out | archivedate = 2013-10-29 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029194132/http://www.staradvertiser.com/news/20130730__Zapped_Out.html | url = http://www.staradvertiser.com/hawaii-news/zapped-out/ | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | newspaper = Honolulu Star-advertiser | date = 2013-07-30 | author1 = William Cole | author2 = Nanea Kalani | author3 = Rosemarie Bernardo }}</ref>。全州共因闪电导致价值2万4000美元的破坏<ref>{{cite report | author = National Weather Service office in Honolulu, Hawaii | title = Hawaii Event Report: Lightning | archivedate = 2014-01-03 | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | url = http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/stormevents/eventdetails.jsp?id=462046 | work = National Climatic Data Center | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140103100331/http://www.ncdc.noaa.gov/stormevents/eventdetails.jsp?id=462046 | publisher = National Oceanic and Atmospheric Administration | year = 2013 | date =  | dead-url = no }}</ref>。州内还发生六起交通意外，多条道路被迫封闭，但总体破坏程度很轻<ref>{{cite news | title = Impact minimal as force diminishes | url = http://www.staradvertiser.com/hawaii-news/impact-minimal-as-force-diminishes/ | accessdate = 2016-07-19 | newspaper = Hawaii Star Advertiser | date = 2013-07-30 | author = Gordon Y. N. Pang | archivedate = 2013-10-29 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20131029195100/http://www.staradvertiser.com/news/hawaiinews/20130730__Impact_minimal_as_force_diminishes_.html?id=217562531 | deadurl = no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news | title = Tropical Depression Flossie Is Leaving Hawaii After A Night Of Havoc | newspaper = Huffington Post | date = 2013-07-30 | author = Oskar Garcia | deadurl = yes | url = http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/07/30/tropical-depression-flossie_n_3674452.html | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160305074644/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2013/07/30/tropical-depression-flossie_n_3674452.html | archivedate = 2016-03-05 | accessdate = 2016-03-05 }}</ref>。

